  ORDER_FETCH_SUCCESS: `ORDER_FETCH_SUCCESS`,
  ORDER_FETCH_FAIL: `ORDER_FETCH_FAIL`,

  ORDER_DETAILS_FETCH_REQUEST: `ORDER_DETAILS_FETCH_REQUEST`,
  ORDER_DETAILS_FETCH_SUCCESS: `ORDER_DETAILS_FETCH_SUCCESS`,
  ORDER_DETAILS_FETCH_FAIL: `ORDER_DETAILS_FETCH_FAIL`,
